<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  Japanese (ja) localization for the Bao Translate product surface (bao_* / cd_* keys).
  Notes:
   - Brand "Bao Translate" and technical proper nouns (Sherpa-ONNX, Whisper, Kokoro, Qwen, Gemma,
     Parakeet, Silero VAD, OpenVoice, Supertonic, Zipformer, LiteRT-LM, ONNX, STT/ASR/TTS/VAD,
     Bluetooth/BLE/A2DP/SCO/HFP, Wi-Fi) are intentionally left untranslated.
   - Format specifiers (%1$s, %2$d, %1$.1f, …) are preserved; arg order kept where natural.
   - The per-language voice-enrollment prompt samples (bao_translate_record_prompt*) are deliberately
     NOT overridden here — they are language samples selected by recording language, not UI chrome,
     so they fall back to the default (correct-per-language) values.
-->
